'''謝臣·达尼·巴塔利亚·馬田斯'''（{{lang-pt|Gelson Dany Batalha Martins}}，{{IPA-pt|ˈʒɛɫson mɐɾˈtĩʃ}}，{{bd|1995年|5月11日}}），[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]職業足球員，司職翼鋒，目前效力於[[法甲|法甲]]球隊[[摩納哥體育會足球會|摩納哥]]。

== 球會生涯 ==
=== 士砵亭 ===
馬田斯於[[佛得角|佛得角]][[普拉亞|普拉亞]]出生，其後移民至[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]，並加入{{link-en|C.F.賓菲加|C.F. Benfica|}}和[[葡萄牙士砵亭俱樂部|士砵亭]]的青年軍。2014年3月，他成為[[葡萄牙士砵亭俱樂部|士砵亭]]B隊的成員，簽下一份直至2019年的合約，合約中設有4,500萬歐元的毀約金條款<ref>{{cite web|url=http://asemana.publ.cv/spip.php?article97714&ak=1|title=Gelson Martins renova com Sporting até 2019|trans_title=Gelson Martins renews with Sporting until 2019|publisher=A Semana|language=Pt|date=2014-03-17|accessdate=2014-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826114513/http://asemana.publ.cv/spip.php?article97714&ak=1|archive-date=2014-08-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。對陣{{link-en|科英布拉聯足球會|C.F. União de Coimbra}}時所攻入的一球，受很多人稱讚<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.noticias-do-futebol.com/content/poker-de-bald-em-goleada-tardia|title=Poker de Baldé em goleada tardia|trans_title=Baldé poker in late routing|publisher=Notícias do Futebol|language=Pt|date=|accessdate=2014-08-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826113207/http://www.noticias-do-futebol.com/content/poker-de-bald-em-goleada-tardia|archivedate=2014-08-26}}</ref>，但時任士砵亭B隊的教練卻表示，馬田斯並非出任他擅長的翼鋒，會使他的生涯受影響<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.noticias-do-futebol.com/content/gelson-valoriza-import-ncia-da-academia|title=Gelson valoriza importância da Academia|trans_title=Gelson values importance of the academy|publisher=Notícias do Futebol|language=Pt|date=2014|accessdate=2014-08-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826160830/http://www.noticias-do-futebol.com/content/gelson-valoriza-import-ncia-da-academia|archivedate=2014-08-26}}</ref>。

2014年8月24日，馬田斯為士砵亭B隊首次上陣。他在聯賽對陣[[欧汉尼斯体育俱乐部|奧漢倫斯]]時後備入替，協助球隊作客以1比0勝出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.record.xl.pt/futebol/nacional/liga-honra/detalhe/olhanense-sporting-b-0-1-drame-marca-e-acaba-expulso-901301.html|title=Olhanense-Sporting B, 0−1: Dramé marca e acaba expulso|trans_title=Olhanense-Sporting B, 0−1: Dramé scores and ends up being sent off|publisher=Record|language=Pt|date=2014-08-24|accessdate=2015-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924152907/http://www.record.xl.pt/futebol/nacional/liga-honra/detalhe/olhanense-sporting-b-0-1-drame-marca-e-acaba-expulso-901301.html|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。12月21日，他在對陣[[維多利亞甘馬雷斯B隊|維多利亞甘馬雷斯B隊]]時，攻入職業生涯首個入球，協助球隊以3比1勝出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.record.xl.pt/futebol/nacional/liga-honra/detalhe/v-guimaraes-b-sporting-b-1-3-terceira-vitoria-seguida-para-os-leoes-921447.html|title=V. Guimarães B-Sporting B, 1−3: Terceira vitória seguida para os leões|trans_title=V. Guimarães B-Sporting B, 1−3: Third win in a row for the lions|publisher=Record|language=Pt|date=2014-12-21|accessdate=2015-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924152946/http://www.record.xl.pt/futebol/nacional/liga-honra/detalhe/v-guimaraes-b-sporting-b-1-3-terceira-vitoria-seguida-para-os-leoes-921447.html|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2015年夏天，馬田斯獲領隊[[佐治·謝蘇斯|佐治·謝蘇斯]]提升至一線隊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.record.xl.pt/futebol/nacional/1a-liga/sporting/detalhe/gelson-de-extremo-da-equipa-b-ao-onze-na-supertaca-964756.html|title=Gelson: de extremo da equipa B ao onze... na Supertaça|trans_title=Gelson: from B-team winger to starting eleven... in Supercup|publisher=Record|language=Pt|date=2015-07-26|accessdate=2015-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924152530/http://www.record.xl.pt/futebol/nacional/1a-liga/sporting/detalhe/gelson-de-extremo-da-equipa-b-ao-onze-na-supertaca-964756.html|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，並於8月9日舉行的[[葡萄牙超級盃|葡萄牙超級盃]]對陣[[里斯本與本菲卡體育|賓菲加]]的賽事中，首次代表一線隊上陣。他於補時階段入替，協助球隊以1比0勝出，奪得冠軍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rtp.pt/noticias/desporto/supertaca-e-do-sporting_e850342|title=Benfica 0−1 Sporting|publisher=Rádio e Televisão de Portugal|language=Pt|date=2015-08-09|accessdate=2015-08-27|archive-date=2018-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711223610/https://www.rtp.pt/noticias/desporto/supertaca-e-do-sporting_e850342|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年8月14日，馬田斯在對陣[[唐迪拉體育會|唐迪拉體育會]]時，第89分鐘後備入替，完成一線隊聯賽首戰<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dn.pt/desporto/sporting/interior/penalti-no-final-salvou-sporting-frente-ao-estreante-tondela-4729343.html|title=Penálti no final salvou Sporting frente ao estreante Tondela|trans_title=Penalty in the end saved Sporting against newcomer Tondela|publisher=Diário de Notícias|language=Pt|date=2015-08-14|accessdate=2016-01-16|archive-date=2016-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160222174528/http://www.dn.pt/desporto/sporting/interior/penalti-no-final-salvou-sporting-frente-ao-estreante-tondela-4729343.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。次年1月15日，他在對陣同一隻球隊時攻入一球。此入球為士砵亭在聯賽攻入的第五千球，最終球隊以2比2打平對手<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.record.xl.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sporting/detalhe/gelson-martins-apontou-o-golo-5000-dos-leoes-na-liga.html|title=Gelson Martins apontou o golo 5000 dos leões na Liga|trans_title=Gelson Martins scored the lions' goal 5000 in League|publisher=Record|language=Pt|date=2016-01-15|accessdate=2016-01-16|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306044958/http://www.record.xl.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sporting/detalhe/gelson-martins-apontou-o-golo-5000-dos-leoes-na-liga.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

=== 馬德里體育會 ===
2018年7月18日，馬丁斯接受了馬德里競技的邀請。一周後，他在同意達成一項為期五年的協議後被宣佈為西班牙俱樂部的新球員。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://en.as.com/en/2018/07/18/football/1531913772_113769.html |title=Atlético wait for an answer from FIFA on Gelson Martins |publisher=Diario AS |date=18 June 2018 |accessdate=18 June 2018 |archive-date=2018-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180726005330/https://en.as.com/en/2018/07/18/football/1531913772_113769.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 國家隊生涯 ==
2014年，馬田斯曾代表{{link-en|葡萄牙19歲以下國家足球隊|Portugal national under-19 football team|葡萄牙 U19}}出戰，參加[[歐洲U-19足球錦標賽|歐洲U-19足球錦標賽]]，他上陣全部賽事，最終[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]隊得到亞軍席位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://economico.sapo.pt/noticias/ser-jogador-nao-e-tudo-para-os-vicecampeoes-europeus-sub19_198891.html|title=Ser jogador não é tudo para os vice-campeões europeus Sub-19|trans_title=Being a player is not all to Under-19 European vice-champions|publisher=Económico|language=Pt|date=2014-08-01|accessdate=2014-08-25|archive-date=2014-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826114847/http://economico.sapo.pt/noticias/ser-jogador-nao-e-tudo-para-os-vicecampeoes-europeus-sub19_198891.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。馬田斯亦曾參加[[2015年國際足協U-20世界盃|2015年國際足協U-20世界盃]]，並在分組賽對陣{{link-en|塞內加爾20歲以下國家足球隊|Senegal national under-20 football team|塞內加爾 U20}}以及十六強對陣{{link-en|紐西蘭20歲以下國家足球隊|New Zealand national under-20 football team|紐西蘭 U20}}時皆有入球<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.fifa.com/u20worldcup/matches/round=271602/match=300269544/match-report.html|title=Dominant Portugal defeat Senegal|publisher=FIFA.com|date=2015-05-31|accessdate=2015-08-27|language=en|archive-date=2015-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150910123918/http://www.fifa.com/u20worldcup/matches/round=271602/match=300269544/match-report.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.fifa.com/u20worldcup/matches/round=271600/match=300269530/match-report.html|title=Portugal break hosts' hearts|publisher=FIFA.com|date=2015-06-11|accessdate=2015-08-27|language=en|archive-date=2015-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906064655/http://www.fifa.com/u20worldcup/matches/round=271600/match=300269530/match-report.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，可是球隊於八強出局<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.fifa.com/u20worldcup/matches/round=271598/match=300269537/match-report.html|title=Brazil through as profligate Portugal pay the penalty|publisher=FIFA.com|date=2015-06-14|accessdate=2015-08-27|language=en|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923184342/http://www.fifa.com/u20worldcup/matches/round=271598/match=300269537/match-report.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年9月，在對陣[[安道爾國家足球隊|安道爾國家足球隊]]和[[法羅群島足球代表隊|法羅群島足球代表隊]]時，馬田斯獲[[葡萄牙國家足球隊|葡萄牙國家足球隊]]徵召，有機會出陣[[2018年世界盃足球賽|2018年世界盃足球賽]]外圍賽<ref>{{cite news|url= http://desporto.sapo.pt/futebol/seleccao/portugal/clube-portugal/artigo/2016/09/29/convocados-de-fernando-santos-para-jogos-frente-a-andorra-e-ilhas-faroe|title= Gelson Martins convocado por Fernando Santos|trans_title= Gelson Martins called by Fernando Santos|publisher= SAPO|language= Pt|date= 2016-09-29|accessdate= 2016-10-04|archive-date= 2016-10-02|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20161002034907/http://desporto.sapo.pt/futebol/seleccao/portugal/clube-portugal/artigo/2016/09/29/convocados-de-fernando-santos-para-jogos-frente-a-andorra-e-ilhas-faroe|dead-url= no}}</ref>。在對陣安道爾時，馬田斯首次代表國家隊上陣，於第72分鐘後備入替[[比比|比比]]，葡萄牙最終以6比0大勝對手<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3827770/Portugal-6-0-Andorra-Cristiano-Ronaldo-scores-FOUR-rout-minnows-two-men-sent-kicking-Real-Madrid-star.html|title=Portugal 6–0 Andorra: Cristiano Ronaldo nets FOUR in rout as minnows have two men sent off for kicking Real Madrid star during World Cup qualifier|publisher=Daily Mail|date=2016-10-07|accessdate=2016-10-09|language=en|archive-date=2016-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021050636/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3827770/Portugal-6-0-Andorra-Cristiano-Ronaldo-scores-FOUR-rout-minnows-two-men-sent-kicking-Real-Madrid-star.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 比賽風格 ==
馬田斯原本在場上的位置為一名右翼鋒，他亦能出任左翼鋒的位置。在青年國家隊時，他在場上的位置為一名右閘<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.noticias-do-futebol.com/content/gelson-surpreende-em-todos-os-aspectos|title=Gelson surpreende em todos os aspectos|trans_title=Gelson surprises in every aspect|publisher=Notícias do Futebol|language=Pt|date=|accessdate=2014-08-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826115515/http://www.noticias-do-futebol.com/content/gelson-surpreende-em-todos-os-aspectos|archivedate=2014-08-26}}</ref>。

